result:
div.padding-large
  div.flex.wide.justify-space-between
    //- :Left
    div: h2 Packages

    //- Right
    div: button(@click='$refs.newpackage.show()') New Package
  
  //- Contents
  table.wide
    tr
      td
        h3 Newborn Packages
        span Short Description
      td
        button.float-right Edit
    tr
      td
        h3 Newborn Packages
        span Short Description
      td
        button.float-right(@click='$refs.editpackage.show()') Edit

  modal(ref="newpackage" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding New Package
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            form.grid-1-small.grid-2-medium-plus.align-center
              label Package Name
              input
              label Category
              select
                option Newborn Fake
                option Fake Regular
              label Package Price
              input
              label Package Description
              input
              label Duration
              input
              label # of Themes
              input
              label Active
              label.padding
                input(type="checkbox")
                span Active
              details.span-2-medium-plus
                summary Inclusions
                div.flex.wide.align-center
                  select.flex-grow
                    option Inclusion 1
                    option Inclusion 2
                  button Add
                table.wide
                  tr
                    td Inclusion 1
                    td.float-right
                      a X
              div.flex.wide
                button Cancel
                button Add Package

  modal(ref="editpackage" inline-template)
        div
          transition(name='fade')
            #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
          transition(name='fade')
            #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.max-high
              div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
                h2.padding Edit Package
                a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
              hr
              div.padding.overflow-auto
                form.grid-1-small.grid-2-medium-plus.align-center
                  label Package Name
                  input
                  label Category
                  select
                    option Newborn Fake
                    option Fake Regular
                  label Package Price
                  input
                  label Package Description
                  input
                  label Duration
                  input
                  label # of Themes
                  input
                  label Active
                  label.padding
                    input(type="checkbox")
                    span Active
                  details.span-2-medium-plus
                    summary Inclusions
                    div.flex.wide.align-center
                      select.flex-grow
                        option Inclusion 1
                        option Inclusion 2
                      button Add
                    table.wide
                      tr
                        td Inclusion 1
                        td.float-right
                          a X
                  div.flex.wide
                    button Delete
                    button Edit Package
